data.description: Presenting the Carmel, a delightful vineyard home incorporating all the latest and greatest design elements. Simply stated, every inch of this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, plus den, solar home is breathtakingly beautiful. The upgrades are plentiful, including modern farmhouse exterior, gorgeous walnut engineered hardwood flooring, designer paint/wallpaper, custom light fixtures, plantation shutters, plus, front and center is a spectacular vineyard/mountain view featuring a large serene pond with water fountain. An inviting courtyard entrance begins your journey - it’s the perfect spot to gather with a glass of local wine and enjoy the Central Coast sunsets. Inside, the open-concept kitchen/great room/dining area surrounds the outdoor entertaining space, lending itself to seamless indoor/outdoor get-togethers. The culinary kitchen is the heartbeat of the home with stunning quartz countertops and waterfall island with dramatic hammered brass dome pendant lighting, white Shaker-style cabinetry, gas cooktop, wall ovens, rich gray tile backsplash, spacious walk-in pantry, and GE stainless appliances - it’s a chefs delight! Large parties or small gatherings, this space can handle it - start off with appetizers on the island, serve the main event in the dining room outfitted with a stunning modern crystal chandelier, then retire to the great room around the custom Spanish tiled fireplace (all spaces offer incredible views) - or take it outside to the covered patio with motorized retractable screen and cozy up to the built-in gas fire table. When family and friends are staying over, you’ll have plenty of room - two well-designed bright and sunny bedrooms with a full shared bath. Once your guests are comfortably tucked away, head to the owner’s suite, your personal retreat from the world - a spacious bedroom with spectacular sunrise views, and a spa-like master bath with exquisitely tiled shower, Roman tub, dual sinks with vanity, linen storage, and a giant walk-in closet. In addition, there’s a fully-outfitted SmartSpace/laundry - a quiet place to work from home or enjoy your favorite hobby; a Londonesque powder room and a gorgeous den/office with built-in library. Add a 2-car garage with built-in storage, a separate garage with a state-of-the-art TONAL workout station, A/C, wireless security camera, and low-maintenance landscaping. You’ll never want to leave this impeccably designed home, but when you do, you’ll enjoy all the amenities Trilogy life has to offer.
